        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天上神仙府，人间宰相家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哪一个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷我叫你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么话。原来是孙降。你到此则甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问你老人家，太师爷可在府中？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
