          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（范太师上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告老归林，无事站在书院。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀太师：外有孙降求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙降，太师传你，随我进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太师传我，谢谢你老人家。这位大爷，好一位大爷，要抵得人家十七八位大爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何抵得许多？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你好得很，但愿你来世还在他家做这官大爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡说。见过太师。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n丢下米口袋，放下竹竿来，掸掸灰尘。太师爷在上，孙降作个揖，磕一个头，\n请个安，站在一旁，垂两只手，听太师爷的吩咐，我连动也不敢动。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙降，老夫未曾发放与你，你为何胆大自己爬起？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老太师原是贵人，原有贵体，开了贵口，岂不上了元气。小花子代吩咐一声，\n岂不是一样乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔一向还好？住在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住在没头古寺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "饮食如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每日找有烟囱的食食。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "食些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "食不尽诗云、子曰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "穿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "穿不尽之乎者也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看尔不出，倒有一派儒家气象。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀太师：小花子虽不算文章华国，亦算诗礼传家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你何不谋一堂门馆，教传教传？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀太师：你老人家独坐朝纲，不知外面的光景。日下读书者少，教馆者多，英\n雄无奈，何来用我这支笔乎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔前来则甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "磕头讨赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫无物可赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小花子自求一箪食，一瓢饮，在陋巷人不堪其忧，回也不改其乐。老太师说什\n么无物可赏乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好话多讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诗三百一言以蔽之。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "西廊候赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢太师。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。我这才是贤哉回也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙降下。吕蒙正上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天地与人分厚薄，世上多少不均匀。富贵之家常富贵，似我贫穷——"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "更贫穷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生吕蒙正。闻听范老太师告老归林，府中俸禄，堆积如山，不免腆着脸儿前\n去讨求周济。行行走走，走走行行。来此已是。\n门上哪位大哥在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又是哪一个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是吕相公，到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问大哥，太师可在府中？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正在高厅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "烦劳大哥与我通禀，后学吕求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请少站。\n太师，醇安吕求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可是那吕蒙正？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他的身上如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是照旧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这小畜生，还不发愤攻读，还是照常。传话出去，老夫一路而来，鞍马劳倦，\n今日不见，叫他改日再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕相公，太师传话，一路而来，鞍马劳倦，今日不见，叫你改日再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有晚生帖儿一张，后有告老林泉诗词一首，烦劳大哥与我投递。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n禀太师：吕相公有晚生帖儿一张，后有告老林泉诗词一首，太师请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呈上来！哎呀！这小畜生，人虽贫穷，倒有一笔好字。请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕相公，太师传你，随我进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙降暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，把我放在这里，也不命人来发放于我。我好有一比：蚊子叮碳，叮到晚，\n饿到黑。我要出去看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙降撞吕蒙正。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又是谁？哎呀，原来是吕相公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙大哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公到此则甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我么，前来投亲的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看你不出，人虽贫穷，倒有这门高亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，相公请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是投亲的，你请！回来再见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是亲不是亲，心里见分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老太师在上，学生醇安吕拜揖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不曾听见。老太师在上，学生醇安吕重见一礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不对不对，不是前来投亲，分明与我一样，前来讨求周济。要是亲么，他行了\n二礼，连一礼不答。\n相公，有道，乞丐不可并行，这点小意思，被你挤挤赶赶，还是赶掉了。想你\n君子固穷，我小人穷斯滥矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙降下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "学生连行二礼，老太师一礼不答，岂待斯文乡里之道乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想老夫受了多少官员礼拜，何况你一介贫生？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老太师道学生一介贫生。昔日班超不遇，投奔任尚；韩信未遇，受辱胯下。学\n生虽不必二贤，老太师可比作任尚乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你拿老夫比作任尚，尔比二贤，想你后来亦没有三齐王之福。进前听训！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "谁叫你玷辱斯文？\n有何脸面站立在前厅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "老太师暂息雷霆怒，\n学生言来禀告你闻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老太师，千日富贵亦有一日不富贵。学生千日贫穷亦有一日富贵。想世间上贫\n富二字，最难料的啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "我蒙正胸藏韬略口吐奇文，\n老太师只重衣冠不重人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "休夸你胸藏韬略口吐奇文，\n吕蒙正痴痴呆呆、肩担水桶、失落一头，轻重不留神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "天下斯文同骨肉，\n还念他祖上是公卿，把银多赠——"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "休多赠，\n怕他下次又来临。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，赏他升米十文。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕相公，太师赏你升米十文。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是不要。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀太师，他不要。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凭他去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙降上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把我放在这里，我倒放心不下，出去看看，又是哪一个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是吕相公，你还不曾出去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未曾出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公你也不是前来投亲的，与我孙降一样，前来讨求周济。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说也惭愧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "常言说得好：乞丐不可并行。我在里面，你就不该来，这点小意思，被你赶赶\n挤挤赶掉了。想你君子固穷，我小人穷斯滥矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说也惭愧得紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要紧。但不知老太师周济你些什么东西？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "升米十文。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可曾要他的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未曾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，慢说给你不要，就是给我也是不要。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却是为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还失了我讨饭之人的锐气。想你这等文人，进得相府，讨求周济，或银子助你\n三两五两，或米助你三担五担，才是待斯文一脉之道理。一升米，十个钱，一\n不算斋僧，二不算布施，真乃管仲之器小哉，哎呀小哉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何人喧哗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙降。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙降，太师传你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太师传我，我正要见他的很呢。我这个花子，是家门口的花子，不是远方来的。\n他纵有势力，不压于我乡党乎。你站过来，让我去见他。\n孙降伺候老太师。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙降，你为何大胆西廊喧哗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并非小花子在西廊喧哗，你老人家把我放在西廊脚下，言而不言，语而不语，\n也不着人来打发与我。我也不能怪你老人家。但不知吕相公进得相府，你老人\n家周济他些什么东西？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "升米十文。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷子！干干脆脆就是一升米、十个钱，不要文了。要是文字，你就张开嘴吃\n了罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂有此理！想吕相公这等文人，进得相府，讨求周济。你老人家或米助他三担\n五担，或银子助他三两五两，就是小花子在外面，也好与你扬扬名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫岂要你扬名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么岂要我扬名？你身居宰相，还有一部书未曾读到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫何书不读，哪书不览？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是《论语》上有一篇，你未曾读到？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒要你讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲么就讲，还讲不出来？《论语》云：“原思为之宰，与之粟九百，辞。子曰：\n毋以与尔邻里乡党乎？”你把“乡党”二字，打头上掉了。一升米、十个钱，\n一不算斋僧，二不算布施，真乃管仲之器小哉！老爷子，你真真的小哉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫何以为小哉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么何以为小哉？想吕相公进得相府，连行二礼，你坐在上面安然不动，岂待\n斯文之道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想老夫受了多少官员礼拜，何况他一介贫生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开口道人一介贫生，我问你：你这宰相在老太君龙胎里怀着，养下来就是个太\n师？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黉门所出，书里而得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好哇！亦是黉门所出，书里而得。必须要十载寒窗，九载遨游，八月科场，七\n篇锦绣，鹿鸣宴罢，五经魁首，四杆彩旗，三斗御酒，两朵金花，才得独占鳌\n头，像梯子似的慢慢地一蹬一蹬往上爬。我还只道你在你娘肚内做现成的宰相！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赶下去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大不通乎！对不佳人乎！岂有此理乎！外人还要谈乎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下去就下去。你这推推搡搡的做什么？你也不见得在他家一辈子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惭愧呀惭愧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看，吕相公在那旁叹气，我向前说几句好话，与他宽宽心。\n吕相公这里来！你乃是读书人，不要焦心，焦干了心血，不好念文章。我兄弟\n是读而未成，你是拔高往上，我有几句金石良言，你且听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你暂且挨过残冬苦，\n等到春来起卧龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看你红光满面，发达就在眼前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "时来运至腾云起、吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何以见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦啊嗷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看他看财奴有什么收成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说着，说着，说上我一火头来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙大哥，你讲错了，敢是一头的火？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错是一头火，我被他气糊涂了。站过来，让我说他几句。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "由他去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "让我说他几句。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凭他去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！什么由他去，凭他去。我倒明白，你这心思。你怕日后高中，在朝房与老\n头子不好讲话。再也不要说了。我还怕他开道上朝，参掉我这个花子，六部里\n说一声不许我沿街要饭么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "向前来深深埋怨，\n你有那天高大罪名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫何以有天高大罪名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你的罪该韫椟而藏之，还要我鸣鼓而攻之？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒要你讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我讲就讲，怕你拿刀来把我的舌头割了！想你乃周天子驾前托孤老臣。老王爷\n晏驾，你就该扶保幼主登基，才是道理。怎么反将江山一旦付与赵太祖执掌？\n你再隐居林下，袖手旁观。人不来骂你，你还敢骂谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休胡闹！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休胡闹！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休罗唣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休罗唣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才狗才骂的何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，赶下去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此地不留人，自有留人处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我只得仰面朝天哭出门厅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范太师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了哇，哈哈哈，罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（范太师、院子同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说不过你，我也不叫孙降。\n你只好进去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，好一个不该来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个吕相公是个书呆子。哎，好一个不该来，你不该来，我也是不该来。吵了\n半天，一个钱也没有看见，早知道也是不该来。哎呀，他倒是好好的一升米，\n十个钱，被我一泡子赶，一泡子吵，打脱掉了，我倒对不住他。我说两句好话\n给他宽宽心。\n吕相公，这里来，你不要在那里生气，我有两个古人说来你听听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙大哥讲古哇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是乱道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔日班超不遇，投奔任尚；韩信未遇，受辱胯下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伍子胥也曾吹过箫，这一辈贤人，皆是先贫而后富，何况你我乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕蒙正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙大哥，他们乃前辈老先生，我们比他不上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙降",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说远了，比不上，讲个近的。昔日天理门街上，有个卑田院，内中有个郑旦之\n子，名叫郑"
        }
      ],
